1. Ona je bila *nervozna* (She was nervous). 
2. Nervozno je zurila u njega (She stared nervously at him). 
3. Ona je bila prenervozna da bi pričala o tome (She was too nervous to talk about it). 
4. On je bio *nervozan* (He was nervous).
5. Nervozno se smejala (She laughed nervously). 
6. Ona se nervozno okrenula prema njemu (She nervously turned towards him).